      <body>
         <div type="edition"><!-- transcription goes here -->
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="slaveName" key="Herma">Her<hi rend="ligature">ma</hi>
                  </name>
               </persName>
               <persName>
                  <name type="slaveName" key="Megiste">
                     <hi rend="ligature">Me</hi>gisteni</name>
               </persName>
               <lb n="2"/>contubernali
                    <lb n="3"/>suae carissim<hi rend="ligature">ae</hi>
               <lb n="4"/>fecit tumulum.</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>"Herma made this tomb for Megiste, his most dear wife."</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary"><!-- notes go here -->
            <p>Interpuncts between every word, except at line ends. Bottom
                    two-thirds of stone bare of any writing.</p>
         </div>
